# Day 22: og-image.png is a brand asset rendered from the SVG by
# scripts/build_og_png.py and must ship in the repo so base.html's
# og:image meta tag points at a real file. The package_data glob in
# pyproject.toml (`static/**/*`) bundles it for the deployed app.
!src/rmn_dashboard/static/og-image.png
